** '''Mistag:''' Very well, Grubfoot. You may enter Dorgesh-Kaan, but you must stay with [player name] until you leave.
** '''Grubfoot:''' Thank you, [player name]! I promise I be no trouble.
** '''Player:''' Follow me.
** {{tact|end}}
